      "code": "# search for forms like \"لا تزوجن\" \"اخاك\"\ncand=[]\nfor rec in had:\n    txt = rec.get('hadithTxt') or rec.get('Matn') or ''\n    n=normalize(txt)\n    if \"لا تزوجن\" in n:\n        cand.append(txt)\nlen(cand)",
      "container_id": "cntr_6896726f619c8190ad2147ac5bd4d4270d89ff33c2513782",
