      "code": "# narrow: look for 'تزوج' verb\nhits=[]\nfor rec in had:\n    n=normalize((rec.get('hadithTxt') or rec.get('Matn') or ''))\n    if \"تزوج\" in n and \"اخ\" in n:\n        hits.append((rec['hadithID'], rec.get('hadithTxt') or rec.get('Matn') or ''))\nlen(hits)",
